
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-mpls-lsp-ping-13.txt'>
    <title>"Detecting MPLS Data Plane Failures", Kireeti Kompella, George Swallow</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-mpls-lsp-ping-13.txt</link>
    <description>This document describes a simple and efficient mechanism that can be used to detect data plane failures in Multi-Protocol Label Switching (MPLS) Label Switched Paths (LSPs). There are two parts to this document: information carried in an MPLS "echo request" and "echo reply" for the purposes of fault detection and isolation; and mechanisms for reliably sending the echo reply.</description>
    <dc:date>2006-01-05T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
